title: Google releases latest Wear OS 3.2 developer preview with some very minor tweaks
content:
The next generation of Wear OS is around the corner, with Google slowly progressing on Wear OS 3 through developer previews. This week, the company has quietly released another emulator image, which shows some progress since the last time we dove in.

more…

The post Google releases latest Wear OS 3.2 developer preview with some very minor tweaks appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: The latest update to the Wear OS developer preview introduces Wear OS 3.2, but there aren't many changes to be seen on the surface.
